{"tid":2397544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門黃金海岸第9座被封 政府人員舉中指贈港人","createTime":"2021-02-06T13:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T07:59:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"499426ffbffec211660801cb9865498edb7b7d92","tid":2397544,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/photos/a.104083121451149/206051484587645/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhatsNewsMedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.104083121451149%2F206051484587645%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=e51a2820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/photos/a.104083121451149/206051484587645/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/146229068_206051487920978_7245579279058448696_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=uf6AdQo_PkMAX-FrdC6&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=c893151901e70c5ef0e648a3e42a7ae8&amp;oe=6044567B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F146229068_206051487920978_7245579279058448696_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3Duf6AdQo_PkMAX-FrdC6%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3Dc893151901e70c5ef0e648a3e42a7ae8%26oe%3D6044567B&h=3b198aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[屯門黃金海岸第9座被封<br />\n政府人員舉中指贈港人]<br />\n<br />\n晚上八時半，政府宣布屯門黃金海岸第9座列為受限區域，預計封鎖時間直至明早7時。<br />\n<br />\n宣布過後政府物資及相關人員陸續到達上址，惟一輛載有政府人員的白色小巴駛經一眾傳媒時，一名男士眼神凶狠向窗外高舉中指，猶如敵視全港市民。<br />\n<br />\n作為香港政府的公務員，近日被強迫宣誓效忠政府，但理應服務港人的使命如今猶如蕩然無存。為服務政府進行封區，但態度卻敵視港人，公務員是人民公僕或是淪為政府傀儡？<br />\n<br />\n攝：Jason<br />\n#政府人員 #舉中指 #屯門 #封區<br />\n────────────────<br />\nFacebook：和你報 WhatsNewsMedia<br />\nInstagram：WhatsNewsMedia<br />\nTelegram：和你報WhatsNews Media<br />\nYouTube：和你報WhatsNews Media<br />\nPayme：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35wA73y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35wA73y&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=a19b2d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35wA73y</a><br />\n報料熱線：+852 59881543(Signal)"},{"pid":"72460879dbe0bf92d8858cd04fc35b1d940debf4","tid":2397544,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"公墓園好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8cefca1d02bb1fc291e9346eaeb933b483c5f3","tid":2397544,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d524e41f219500155362b20a3c2bf689bbf6f6e7","tid":2397544,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6982268202461af0abbe02bfffce6b2ace9a4d","tid":2397544,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31cd244201d22fcb3417a42d50a34e3d251ea75","tid":2397544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7cdeda687bab6a6f75b3c31611bef907cc7927","tid":2397544,"uid":179606,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"佢可能係抽籤抽中左被迫黎